      <title>由於囊性纖維化治療的強勁需求，Vertex 超越第一季利潤預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/vertex-tops-q1-profit-estimates-robust-demand-cystic-fibrosis-treatments-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於囊性纖維化治療藥物的強勁應用，福泰製藥 (Vertex Pharmaceuticals) 週一第一季利潤超出了華爾街預期。]]></description>
