      <title>由於對第三季消費者需求的擔憂，泰森食品股價下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tyson-foods-beats-profit-estimates-cost-control-efforts-sales-slip-2024-05-06/</link>
